dimensionless variables $x'=2k x$ and $t'=\omega t$. Using
$\mu= \frac{m\omega^{2}}{2V_{S}k^{2}}$, $\nu=2k d$, 
$\gamma_V=\frac{V_C}{V_S}$, we get the equation of motion
